messages.text: Is this Eve Childs?
Who is this?
Jess Kane. Are you the sister of Adrienne Childs?
WHAT DO YOU KNOW ABOUT MY SISTER???
Whoa there! First, that she’s been missing, and second, that she probably looks a lot like my friend Emily
That about right?
Oh my God, yes!  Who are you?? How did you get my number??
I know where your sister is
Yes, I know too
How do you know!?
First tell me how you got my number, and I’ll tell you what I know
My friend Emily escaped this lab experiment…
She was the one that got away!
How do you know about her? ARE YOU IN ON THIS!?
NO!! My friend Anna saw her escape when she tried to save my sister
Well, she escaped but she got caught again.
Before she did she gave me the number for this doctor Angela Smith and said to contact her to get her help
And this woman gave you my number??
Well, I had my friend hack into her computer and among other things she had a master list for all the girls involved
The clones, you mean
Yeah, I can’t really take myself seriously when I say that bonkers as shit word. But anyway.
You lived the closest to me and were the only one who was a sibling.
The others were only children, and I know the parents are in on things, so…you know where they are?
Do you know how to get in?
My friend is inside right now in disguise
What!?
As a soldier…long story
So then you know we have to get them the hell out of there ASAP.
The doctor told me they’re doing crazy ass experiments on them
Wait you talked to her too?? What else did she say??? Is she with her now???
No, she was part of the original team that founded the project. Lazarus Sciences they were called.
It was illegal and when the government found out they seized almost all of her research...
and then took all the girls back in for tests
Can she help us get them out??
She said they are banning her from being near them, and threatened her family if she spoke out about it...
but managed to give me the name Otto Jacobs...
who apparently was also originally on the project that they’re holding there.
She said if I see him and mention her name, and he might help
So you were planning on trying to bust them out? How?
My hacker friend The Monkey…I was going to have him hack into their security system...
and then I was going to wing it from there
Wing it?? You can’t wing it
Yeah, well you said you have your friend Anna on the inside, right?? Maybe she can help
Yes, she knows where the girls are
You know there are like 40 right?
Yeah…we should probably try to save just the ones we know, then try to get the others later
We can’t do that. The doctor said they are injecting them with diseases and dissecting them and shit
But what if we mess up? Then we lose everyone
Listen, I can’t live with that shit on my conscience. We have to try all of them
I know this bloke Teddy who drives a bus.
They are going to notice us driving a bus onto the property
So we park the bus far away from the property
What kind of bus is it?
A school bus. Its painted with all the signs of the zodiac and might only really be used to go to these hippy retreat things...
but it works
And so we meet him there?
Well, you can stay with him
Why me??
Do you have any experience breaking and entering?
No
Well, let’s say, I have a little experience in the matter
Okay, well let me talk to Anna so we can all link up and figure something out
She seems to know a back way, we might be able to slip them out
Tell her about that Otto guy and the name Dr. Angela Smith
She supposedly cared about the girls
Also, some sort of diversion will have to be made, but we’re probably going to have to coordinate that on the fly
Are you sure your friend can hack into the security system??
Did you ever hear about when that sex video played during that live Fox News broadcast?
before hacking all of their news data, and exposing their lies about the Newland Report??
Yes…
That was The Monkey.
Jesus
I’m going to go get Teddy and the bus.
I’ll meet you at the Burger King on Telly Pike near Biotech so we can coordinate before going in
Okay.  How do I know you’re not in on things?
Well that’s why I’m meeting you at Burger King first.
That and because I always like to have a milkshake in case tonight is the night I get shot. See you there in an hour?
Yes…
I’ll be in the black hoodie
Click below to see what happens next...
